quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  18,85,"So he followed a way."
  18,86,"Until, when he reached the setting place of the sun, he found it setting in a spring of black muddy (or hot) water. And he found near it a people. We (Allâh) said (by inspiration): "
  18,87,"He said: "
  19,46,"He (the father) said: "
  19,47,"Ibrâhîm (Abraham) said: "
  19,48,""
  20,28,""
  20,29,""
  20,30,""
  21,4,"He (Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم) said: "
  21,5,"Nay, they say: "
  21,6,"Not one of the towns (populations), of those which We destroyed, believed before them (though We sent them signs): will they then believe?"